</div>

<div class="wording-numbered">

The constant expressions shall be integer constant expressions.<ins>For a half-open range, the first constant expression shall be less than or equal to the second constant expression.</ins>
</div>


<div class="wording-clause-section-title">
Semantics
</div>

<div class="wording-numbered wording-numbered-4">

The values described by the `...` operator form a *closed range*, which contains all integer values in sequence starting from and including the first, low value, up to and including the second, high value.<sup>123)</sup>
</div>

<ins>
<div class="wording-newnumbered">

The values described by the `..<` operator form a *half-open range*, which contains all integer values in sequence starting from and including the first, low value, up to but not including the second, high value.<sup>123✨)</sup>
</div>
